Subject: Stealthreport URL is down.
Description: https://stealthreport.nhy.hydro.com/ URL is down. Newly renewed certificate is not visible in web portal. We updated the renewed certificate in IIS and MMC, still not reflected. Attached screenshot for reference. It's impacting production. Kindly consider this on priority.
Solution_Comment__c:
On any ticket please ensure that the most basic things are done and done correctly. Do not trust screeshots.

The issue you were having was caused by the wrong port used (8082, and it should be 443).
After rebinding and restarting the service both AIC and Reports are available, as confirmed by you.
